/-!
# Time-translation metric, matter and gauge Noether block on D8

The complete analytic time action integrates one genuine geometric direction,
not every smooth tangent ghost.  Accordingly this file restricts the existing
metric/matter/`U(1)^2` block to the real line generated by time translation.

The only remaining input is that the two pointwise tensor pullback derivatives
are smooth symmetric global sections.  This is the exact dependent-bundle
regularity obstruction left by the present Mathlib API.
-/

namespace JanusFormal
namespace P0EFTJanusMappingTorusTimeTranslationMetricMatterGaugeNoether4D

set_option autoImplicit false
set_option synthInstance.maxHeartbeats 300000

noncomputable section

open scoped Manifold ContDiff
open Bundle
